<div class="index-container">

    <div class="background-img">
        <div class="nav-bar">
            <div class="nav-title">AppName</div>
            <div class="nav-items">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a onclick="document.getElementById('id01').style.display='block'" class="login-ref"
                    style="width:auto;">Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="index-header">

            <div class="header-container">
                <h1>Welcome To <strong id="red-appname">HACK and MAKE</strong></h1>
                <p>We want to help you achieve your goals</p>

                <div class="index-btns">
                    <a href="/viewAll" class="search-ref">View Contests</a>
                    <a onclick="document.getElementById('id02').style.display='block'" class="signup-ref"
                        style="width:auto;">Signup</a>
                </div>
            </div>



        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="id01" class="modal">

        <form class="modal-content animate" action="/auth/login" method="POST">
            <div class="imgcontainer">
                <span onclick="document.getElementById('id01').style.display='none'" class="close"
                    title="Close Modal">&times;</span>
                <img src="../images/default.png" alt="Avatar" class="avatar">
            </div>

            <div class="container-form">
                <label for="username"><b>Username</b></label>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Enter Username" name="email" required>

                <label for="password"><b>Password</b></label>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" required>

                <button type="submit">Login</button>

            </div>

            <div class="container" style="background-color:#f1f1f1">
                <button type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('id01').style.display='none'"
                    class="cancelbtn">Cancel</button>
                <span class="password">Forgot <a href="#">password?</a></span>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div id="id02" class="modal">

        <form class="modal-content animate" action="/auth/signup" method="POST">
            <div class="imgcontainer">
                <span onclick="document.getElementById('id02').style.display='none'" class="close"
                    title="Close Modal">&times;</span>
                <h1>Sign Up</h1>
                <p>Please fill in this form to create an account.</p>
                <hr>

            </div>

            <div class="container-form">

                <label for="text"><b>Firstname</b></label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Firstname" name="firstName" required>

                <label for="text"><b>Lastname</b></label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Lastname" name="lastName" required>
                <label for="email"><b>Email</b></label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Email" name="email" required>


                <label for="password"><b>Password</b></label>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" required>

                {{#if err}}
                <p>{{err.message}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                <button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
            </div>

            <div class="container" style="background-color:#f1f1f1">
                <button type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('id02').style.display='none'"
                    class="cancelbtn">Cancel</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>



    <div class="about">
        <div class="about-box">
            <i class="fa fa-money" style="font-size:175px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p>I have the skill, but not the money. This is a great chance to show your skills to a company</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-box">
            <i class="fa fa-building" style="font-size:175px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p>Companies will be holding hackatons, contests, and more to see who fits their style best.</p>

        </div>
        <div class="about-box">
            <i class="fa fa-file-text" style="font-size:175px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <p>Find the contest that best suits your experience, fill out a form and participate</p>

        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="contact">
        <div class="contact-form">
            <div class="contact-title">
                <h1>Contact Us</h1>

            </div>
            <form action="" class="contact-form-box">
                <div class="form-row">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Name" id="contact-name">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Email" id="contact-email">
                </div>
                <div class="form-message">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Message" id="contact-message"><br>
                </div>
                <div class="form-button">
                    <button type="submit">SEND MESSAGE</button>

                </div>

            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>